  "an11.992-1151:1.25": "For the letting go of negligence, these eleven things should be developed.” ",
  "an11.992-1151:2.1": "That is what the Buddha said. ",
  "an11.992-1151:2.2": "Satisfied, the mendicants approved what the Buddha said. ",
